  "summaries": [
    "<b>Copper Brick</b> is a type of <linked>Brick</linked> and an aesthetic building material. Like the ore used to make it, placed Copper Bricks will sparkle. As copper becomes fairly useless quite early in the game, this is an inexpensive ore brick to build with. Despite being made of <linked>Copper</linked>, it has no sell value, as with most other bricks. <linked>Copper Plating</linked> is also available as a decorative block, with the same ingredients and color but a different texture."
